            opsgenie.AlertPolicyTimeRestrictionRestrictionArgs(
                end_day="tuesday",
                end_hour=7,
                end_min=0,
                start_day="monday",
                start_hour=22,
                start_min=0,
            ),
        ],
    )])
```
